title: Fire Island National Seashore: Patchogue / Headquarters
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Places To Go     Patchogue / Headquarters              Patchogue / Headquarters      Â    Visit Park Headquarters for More Information Fire Island National Seashore Headquarters is located at 120 Laurel Street in Patchogue, on the south shore of Long Island, New York.  Please stop by Monday through Friday from 9:00 am to 4:30 pm to pick up a park brochure or other information.  The America the Beautiful - National Parks and Federal Recreational Lands Pass - Senior Pass* ($10 check or money order - no cash please) and America the Beautiful - National Parks and Federal Recreational Lands Pass - Access Pass** (Free) are issued at park headquarters during regular business hours.   Contact Information Fire Island National Seashore 120 Laurel Street Patchogue, New York 11772-3596 Phone: 631-687-4750 Fax: 631-289-4898
